metadata.name: Yacht Girl VIP Club #1
metadata.description: Yacht Girl VIP Club - Welcome to the VIP Club. For the NFT patron with taste, we offer an extremely exclusive and limited mint of beautiful artworks to enhance your private art collection. This is the first in a series that will never be higher than a hundred NFTs per series and on a monthly release schedule that ensures their rarity in the marketplace. For the discerning collector only, this inaugural series celebrates success with a nautical theme featuring popular cryptocurrency jewelry adorning our lovely model. Please visit yachtgirlvipclub.net to mint your own personal Yacht Girl and join the Club.
